a step of means transmitting output of the first to N-th audio code conversion and transmission means to first to M-th (M is a predetermined integer equal to 1 or larger) transmission lines;
a step of selecting a transmission line for receiving the coded data from among first to M-th (M is a predetermined integer equal to 1 or larger) transmission lines; and
